long_desc.thetext:
With a fresh install of F25, systemd-resolve/systemd-resolved are unusable dues to SELinux denials. It's challenging to test or use tools provided by Fedora's init daemon of choice when our own SELinux policies prevent it's default/recommended behavior :(
